{"type": "article", "id": 43122, "title": "Tiffany 再度推出香水系列，以及，Moschino 涉足美妆 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-18T03:17:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 905, "name": "Dover Street Market"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 2636, "name": "Swatch"}, {"id": 8765, "name": "小黄人"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 1864, "name": "Tiffany"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170718105616J3NIGBUAVKE8w1vf.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/puma-raises-full-year-target-second-quarter-sales-10947705/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>PUMA 发布全年业绩预期，第二季度销售额上涨 16%</strong></a> | 第二季度，PUMA 综合销售额增长了 16%，至 9.687 亿欧元，营业利润为 4340 万欧元。该公司将今年全年的运营目标上调至 2.15 亿欧元，预计 2017 年销售额将增长 12％ 至 14％。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cnbc.com/2017/07/17/hm-scraps-monthly-sales-figures-but-promises-more-transparency.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>H&amp;M 六月销售额增长了 7%，以后将不再公布月度数据</strong></a> | 周一，H&amp;M 发布六月业绩，本地货币计其全球销售额同比上升 7%。集团同时表示，从本月起将不会再公布月度财务数据。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/fragrance/tiffany-co-coty-refocus-on-fragrance-10947220/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Tiffany&amp;Co 15 年来首次推出香水系列</strong></a> | 该香水是 Tiffany 与 Coty 集团的首次合作， Tiffany 也是 Coty 集团旗下目前唯一的珠宝品牌，后者拥有 Tiffany 的香水许可权。这款香水将于 8 月 1 日率先登陆纽约 59 街 Bloomingdale 百货和旗舰店，10 月 1 日在全球发售，定价为 75 至 132 美元，同步发售的还有身体乳和沐浴露。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103608yfkKmOMvipXP1VWJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>Dover Street Market New York 最近展示了一款在今年一月份 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/comme-des-garcons-nike-air-force-1-dsmny\" rel=\"nofollow\">CdG 秀场上展示的 Nike Air Force 1 的定制化设计鞋款</a>。这双鞋共有纯黑和纯白两种，鞋头部分加了像是模具的配件。但目前还没有具体发售信息。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103945gwisFVCcRJ1yE0bl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103945Y4HA8tSIDVWs3J0B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>7 月 21 日起，<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-07-17/swatch-x-you/gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Swatch 将在日本发售全新 Swatch X You DIY 手表系列</a>。该系列手表包括 34mm 和 41mm 不同配色的表盘，多种颜色表带、盒子可选，可以自行搭配组合，售价在 8100 至 12600 日元之间。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707181038595iYtTCJDAkd0Ka9p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707181039125bMgwOpu8SCVZkKX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.109091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103913yERoHOWc4Uu0MzLS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707181039149EZMcP4QRwdGx5oX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.109091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103912jhYBfxcX1EaIJ4zu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.100000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071810391209oBT6i4Zme3UAXk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.877273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103920oHGcPMwIpiJbZOLX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.803030\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103919nsozfAGMyYPwXRhE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.057576\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103919RMU49mrvkta0i6W8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.963636\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103919sna8fjrNvDAHSlIc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.951515\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103920Wj8zpFBLvEHO1qQr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.059091\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103920XBYMlbec21gZWiDy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.090909\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707181039248QNisE7FlAgmhW1G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.784848\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>赶上小黄人电影上映，<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-07-17/minion-bape/\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 趁势发布了小黄人主题的服饰系列</a>。该系列涵盖了连帽衫、T恤、卫衣、抱枕、tote 包、棒球帽、口罩等多款单品，将于 7 月 19 日正式登陆日本市场。你觉得好看吗？ </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103824FJRVL1MXiSIpEmWd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103824xYHDL8prAN21K4de.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103824qpLbthlHfOB6AN3n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103825Swhe1Q8Cr2ANqFXV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103824wV1viWJBKAfF0xCR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103840AaeLyQYcfTVjWhX2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103840Hf3bS2WgPonTu6kO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103840Ez081sDoNkOqnPlt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103840x4uBqVQDbKjkC5vW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103841s3BRbSXj9ivNzA7G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103841rL2iMuYywTDomH6Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103841AzpiuIKGdVebMgxm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103842vqfl1kKi7dDWnsOg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103841YkD4UZWvFfEL96zh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103846H2qXdSCAakL6je4s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103846fj6kVw2PDYHge4rx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103846u2lEFPfwHo3srmkh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707181038462HGKg5x8vkeBAdWp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103846F9XiQPxAIzMsf7Wq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103846zcqFBHiVRMA70aCP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103847Ad9vaTCLnzEOYw3h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103847hgVksZa6MLdE3HqU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103847hqs7CVL2vuNHEbQm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/07/17/disney-star-wars-resort/\" rel=\"nofollow\">迪士尼公布了几张星战主题乐园的效果图</a>。迪士尼的 Bob Chapek 透露，该主题乐园是一种全新的讲故事方式，它将作为全新的迪士尼 360 度假村的一部分亮相。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103801ShPJ3kjzcsgxebTA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103801eChko84VZWSjwtfn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707181038084X6BuSVHAch5MENr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>墨尔本球鞋定制单位<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/bespokeind-gundam-asics-gel-lyte-iii-custom\" rel=\"nofollow\"> BespokeIND </a>近日又为经典的 ASICS Tiger GEL-Lyte III 带来了以高达为灵感的定制设计。从高达上提取了蓝、黄、紫多种配色，鞋身则采用了小牛皮、袋鼠皮和鹿皮结合打造。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718105655jPQ1hoYsuUH8plqL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718105652t4q6y950QeMahor2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718105652pJyFWPatLfzoC5Te.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718105651KrzNMeg9yvGCm2PF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.refinery29.com/2017/07/163432/moschino-teddy-bear-makeup-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moschino 也开始做美妆</a>。8 月份，它将会推出和丝芙兰合作的美妆系列，以 Moschino 的 teddy bear 包装形象出现，价格在 28-68 美元之间。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103745DIlqd6nJeNH9cjgu.png\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103742wlHNy9peWaRAo7dU.png\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103742WJCOVkj1pgYKTbq6.png\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103742ha2XeDxnCTNKvEMz.png\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170718103749dvHkycUEfX1LIPYS.png\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/bespokeind-gundam-asics-gel-lyte-iii-custom\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}